Title: An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Ventinilla East in the Municipality of Sta. Barbara, Province of Pangasinan, to Barangay Primicias
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 602
An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Ventinilla East in the Municipality of Sta. Barbara, Province of Pangasinan, to Barangay Primicias
Section 1. The name of Barangay Ventinilla East in the Municipality of Sta. Barbara, Province of Pangasinan, is changed to Barangay Primicias.1Ã¢wphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: June 24, 1983
